               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">DESCRIPTION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Nystatin Ointment USP, for topical use only, contains 100,000 USP Nystatin Units per gram, in a polyethylene and mineral oil base. The structural formula is as follows:</paragraph>
